				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BB%8Bnh-Gi%E1%BA%A3i/B%E1%BA%A1ch-V%C3%A2n-%C4%91%E1%BA%A1o-trung/poem--CIuNLvhtywmMmAjqZthzw">Bạch Vân đạo trung - 白雲道中</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BB%8Bnh-Gi%E1%BA%A3i/author-try44H72AY-hBcH61r-NIQ">Trịnh Giải</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-Kh%E1%BA%AFc-C%E1%BA%A9n/B%C3%ADch-nh%C3%A2n-huynh-th%E1%BA%A5t-%C4%91%E1%BA%A1o-h%C3%AD-t%E1%BA%B7ng/poem-ak8-t1bwXqzyZFmiQORYYQ">Bích nhân huynh thất đạo hí tặng - 璧人兄失盜戲贈</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-Kh%E1%BA%AFc-C%E1%BA%A9n/author-YRtbQ4Y_EBSiaNimbo26Cg">Lê Khắc Cẩn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tr%C3%A3i/Long-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1i-nham/poem-ft4PR31_cjpnrptHgoc0hA">Long Đại nham - 龍岱岩</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tr%C3%A3i/author-NlHfXoUXzue8FcsdIodRLQ">Nguyễn Trãi</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Tr%E1%BB%8Dng-Y%C3%AAm/Nh%E1%BA%A1c-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-l%C3%A2u-k%C3%BD/poem-1P4hzNK16Grkfj46UwH1Fg">Nhạc Dương lâu ký - 岳陽樓記</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Tr%E1%BB%8Dng-Y%C3%AAm/author-V2PfiYxdyB2eEu42wOrwSw">Phạm Trọng Yêm</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/Thi%E1%BB%81n-am-t%E1%BB%B1-c%E1%BB%B1u/poem-wVwEZsJUGtPVUMf_6981dw">Thiền am tự cựu - 禪庵寺舊</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/author-14GcnhLjD2ajP0MTgtX13Q">Ngô Thì Nhậm</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-C%C6%A1/Ti%E1%BB%87m-l%C3%A3o/poem-YkYyDihnQXGqx-Ak_QpBrQ">Tiệm lão - 漸老</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-C%C6%A1/author-47tZT1-IZv4K3OJZjbu5ag">Dương Cơ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/T%E1%BB%8Bnh-%C4%91%E1%BA%A7u-li%C3%AAn/poem-QJiw4EujFB7C4dKKWPnRRQ">Tịnh đầu liên - 並頭蓮</a> (<a href